---
title: Caramelized Onion Swissburgs with Roasted Garlic Horseradish Aioli & Broccoli
description: Looking to up your burger game? This version will blow your mind. The savory beef patties are seared until browned, topped with melty Swiss cheese and buttery caramelized onion, and stuffed into toasted potato buns. Of course, no burger would be complete without a decadent sauce—this one combines mayo, roasted garlic, and wasabi (aka horseradish) to create a punchy spread. Pro tip: The aioli also goes great with the crispy potato wedges on the side.
